headline: Sonoco Earnings Miss Estimates in Q4, Sales Increase 2% Y/Y
summary: SON's Q4 top line reflects low single-digit volume gains and the contribution from Eviosys, offset by the impact of the divestiture of Protexic and lower selling prices.
